{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Zhigu Military Exorcist is a fascinating combination of strategy, action and mysticism. Players will plunge into a dark world where ancient evil forces threaten humanity, and only an elite squad of exorcists can fight back this threat. You will take on the role of the commander of this squad, combining modern military technology with ancient rituals of exorcism.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore gloomy locations, fight terrible creatures and discover the secrets of the other world. Every decision will have consequences, from tactical combat strategies to interaction with forces that are beyond human understanding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready for a unique experience where you will not only destroy enemies, but also learn the nature of evil. Your mission is to protect humanity at any cost. Will you be able to cope with the darkness?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Zhigu Military Exorcist is FPS arena shooter against waves of undead and demon armies with different abilities, strong and weak sides.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game includes (is going to be updated):</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Two maps </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- 20 weapons </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- 10 healing item types </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- 5 armor item types</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- one enemy fraction (techno demons) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- techno demon fraction: 8 enemy types </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The tecnho-demons have quite interesting and different mechanics. It is hoped that players will enjoy them.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927030/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733560167","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2927030/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733560167","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/stea